data.description: WOW!! This home is truly move in ready. As you enter the home you will enjoy the brand new Pergola patio added to front of house along with pavers to make this a large front patio. New dual pane windows have been added along with brand new foam insulation blown into the attic to make this a more energy efficient home. With the addition of a new Bosch 3 tonne HVAC unit those monthly electric bills will definitely see the difference. Seller has installed a Tankless hot water heater, a Whole house water conditioning system and a R.O. System under the kitchen sink. If outdoor living is important to you, this home features an enclosed AZ Room/Lanai with an additional large covered patio to enjoy our wonderful AZ weather. New appliances and updated lighting fixtures literally leaves you little to do to make this your own special place.
